Angela Kinsey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Angela_Kinsey 0 Angela Faye Kinsey (born June 25, 1971) is an American actress known for her role as Angela Martin in the NBC television series The Office (2005–2013). Kinsey had a recurring role on the TBS comedy Your Family or Mine and in the Netflix series Haters Back Off.
